::: {.bg-banner-2}

::: {.index-section-heading}
## Writings {.index-h2}

::: {.index-h2-line}
:::
:::

#### Dedicated to sharing information. {.index-h4}


:::{.index-list}

My blog posts cover a vast range of information in the **ecological and geospatial sciences**. You can find everything from quick map breakdowns to full tutorials on data wrangling and visualization. View the entire archive of my posts [here](posts.qmd).

